Concept ACK, how did you catch this?

Could we also do this?
```cpp
CScript GetScriptForDestination(const CTxDestination& dest)
{
    CScript script;

    bool result = boost::apply_visitor(CScriptVisitor(&script), dest);
    assert(result != script.empty());
    return script;
}
```

